<td>
<h3>Translations</h3>
The Bika dictionaries are ready for translation via the easy-to-use web interface at <a class="external-link" href="https://www.transifex.net/projects/p/bika-lims/resource/bika/">Transifex.net</a>. Please see <a class="external-link" href="http://www.bikalabs.com/helpcentre/how-to/transifex">How to translate Gaob Bika 3 </a><br /><br />
<p>Approved new translations will be taken up into future Bika releases but can also be downloaded directly from Transifex<br /><br />The Transifex interface provides a fun way to translate Bika - do so for your language now!</p>
</td>
<td align="center"><a href="https://www.transifex.net/" target="_blank"><img src="https://sw.transifex.net/14/static/charts/images/tx-logo-micro.png" /></a> <a href="https://www.transifex.net/projects/p/bika-lims/resource/bika/" target="_blank" title="See more information on Transifex.net">Top translations: bika-lims » bika</a> <br /><br /> <a class="external-link" href="https://www.transifex.net/projects/p/bika-lims/resource/bika/"><img src="https://www.transifex.net/projects/p/bika-lims/resource/bika/chart/image_png" /></a><br /></td>
